  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="bg-[#F5F5F0] py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">The Alfa Laval NX-314 is a two-phase horizontal decanter centrifuge rated at approximately 30 GPM, designed for separating solids from liquids in applications including hemp/botanical extraction, WVO processing, crude oil tank bottoms, and wastewater sludge. Dolphin Centrifuge supplies the NX-314 as a complete configured system with controls and optional Class 1 Division 2 explosion-proof certification. Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of decanter centrifuge experience.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- NX-314 Overview -->
      <div id="nx-314-overview" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-5">Alfa Laval NX 314 B31-G Two-Phase Decanter Centrifuge</h2>

        <img
          src="/images/alfa-laval-nx-314-decanter-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Decanter-Centrifuge-System-Class-1-Div-2-for-Herbal-Extraction-600.jpg"
          alt="Alfa Laval Decanter Centrifuge System - Class 1 Div 2 for Herbal Extraction"
          width="600"
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
          class="rounded-lg w-full mb-4"
        />
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-6 text-center">Alfa Laval Decanter Centrifuge System — Class 1 Div 2 for Herbal Extraction</p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The Alfa Laval NX 314 <a href="/decanter-centrifuge/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317] font-medium underline">Decanter Centrifuge</a> is a horizontal de-sludging centrifuge built for the two-phase separation of wastewater, crude oil tank bottoms, municipal sludge-thickening, industrial sludge dewatering, paint sludge handling, etc. With a 10 HP Motor, the NX 314 decanter has a bowl RPM of 4,000 and can process 25 GPM of ethanol hemp biomass slurry.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The NX 314 is one of the most versatile decanter centrifuges in the Alfa Laval product line. Its compact 14-inch bowl diameter and 34-inch bowl length make it suitable for a wide range of industrial applications, from municipal wastewater sludge dewatering to edible oil desludging and waste oil recovery. Dolphin Centrifuge supplies fully reconditioned NX 314 decanter centrifuges with complete inspection, testing, and warranty coverage. Each unit undergoes thorough mechanical and process testing before delivery to ensure reliable performance in the field.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-[#F5F5F0] rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <img
              src="/images/alfa-laval-nx-314-decanter-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Decanter-for-WVO-De-Sludging-1000.jpg"
