        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">This system is a plug &amp; play design that includes all ancillary equipment required to operate the decanter centrifuge as a standalone processing station. The modularized design simplifies installation and reduces on-site engineering requirements, allowing operators to begin processing within hours of delivery.</p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-3">Waste Oil / De-Sludging Module Features</h3>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
          <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-[#1B3A5C] text-white">
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Feature / Option</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-left font-semibold">Purpose</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-gray-800">Sludge Conveyor</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Transfer Separated Sludge to Roll-Off Bin</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-gray-800">Clean Fluid Tank w/ Transfer Pump</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Collect &amp; Transfer De-Sludged Oil</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-gray-800">Feed Pump</td>
                <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-700">Transfer Contaminated Oil from the Supply Tank to the Decanter</td>
              </tr>
