        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-3">Sunflower Oil Desludging Module</h3>
        <img
          src="/images/alfa-laval-nx-314-decanter-centrifuge/Sunflower-Oil-Desludging-Decanter-Centrifuge-600.jpg"
